clk: arm: sunxi: Add a new clock driver for sunxi SOCs

This commit implements the base CPU clocks for sunxi devices. It has
been tested using a slightly modified cpufreq driver from the
linux-sunxi 3.0 tree.

Additionally, document the new bindings introduced by this patch.

Idling:
    / # cat /sys/kernel/debug/clk/clk_summary
       clock                        enable_cnt  prepare_cnt  rate
    ---------------------------------------------------------------------
     osc32k                         0           0            32768
     osc24M_fixed                   0           0            24000000
        osc24M                      0           0            24000000
           apb1_mux                 0           0            24000000
              apb1                  0           0            24000000
           pll1                     0           0            60000000
              cpu                   0           0            60000000
                 axi                0           0            60000000
                    ahb             0           0            60000000
                       apb0         0           0            30000000
     dummy                          0           0            0

After "yes >/dev/null &":
    / # cat /sys/kernel/debug/clk/clk_summary
       clock                        enable_cnt  prepare_cnt  rate
    ---------------------------------------------------------------------
     osc32k                         0           0            32768
     osc24M_fixed                   0           0            24000000
        osc24M                      0           0            24000000
           apb1_mux                 0           0            24000000
              apb1                  0           0            24000000
           pll1                     0           0            1008000000
              cpu                   0           0            1008000000
                 axi                0           0            336000000
                    ahb             0           0            168000000
                       apb0         0           0            84000000
     dummy                          0           0            0

